title: Employees at Top AI Labs Fear Safety Is an Afterthought, Report Says
description: A report commissioned by the State Department says workers at some of the world’s top AI companies harbor significant concerns about the safety of their work.

title: Exclusive: U.S. Must Move ‘Decisively’ to Avert ‘Extinction-Level’ Threat From AI, Government-Commissioned Report Says
description: The U.S. government must move 'decisively' to avert an 'extinction-level threat' to humanity from AI, says a government-commissioned report.
